		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />As a quick fix, you may want to consider getting an American VCR deck and see if you can use that as a bridge to your A/V inputs. Just a thought...
<br />
<br />Additionally, you should consider grabbing a 4.5mm external head line security tool for your consoles, as these are both inexpensive and easily purchased on-line.
<br />
<br />-Xious

		

